WEBVTT

00:00:01.002 --> 00:00:03.837
Kriva sam što se u sudoperu skuplja posuđe

00:00:03.861 --> 00:00:05.782
i tamo stoji satima.

00:00:06.518 --> 00:00:08.600
Provjerila sam to s mojim dečkom.

00:00:08.624 --> 00:00:11.251
On tvrdi da se više radi o danima
nego satima,

00:00:11.275 --> 00:00:12.496
ali nije u tome stvar.

00:00:13.035 --> 00:00:15.909
Stvar je u tome da ponekad završim posao

00:00:15.933 --> 00:00:19.743
tek kad ga se nakupi toliko da
prelazi preko ruba sudopera,

00:00:19.767 --> 00:00:21.524
a moj unutarnji čistunac poludi.

00:00:22.730 --> 00:00:25.172
Ovu šarmantnu naviku sam razvila
tijekom studija

00:00:25.196 --> 00:00:26.460
i imala sam tonu isprika.

00:00:27.117 --> 00:00:28.489
"Žurim na predavanja!"

00:00:28.513 --> 00:00:30.604
"To je samo jedan tanjur više u sudoperu!"